mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Friendship mechanic based on Stardew Valley.
The player can increase his friendship level with other townsfolk by using several methods:
 - Talking with people
 - Doing 'Delivery Quests' for them
 - Giving them Gifts.

People can react to gifts in several ways which reflects on the amount of friendship points 
earned by gifting.

After reaching certain amount of friendship points, you unlock hearts up to maximum of 10.
